# Status:  smartthings-cli — 341+ stars on SmartThingsCommunity/
#          smartthings-cli; log4js — 5,800+ stars on log4js-node/
#          log4js-node, ~50M weekly npm downloads, foundational
#          dependency of didi/xiaoju-survey (3.8k stars) +
#          brookshi/Hitchhiker (2.2k stars) + lisong/code-push-
#          server (1.9k stars) + hengliyin/cdfang-spider (1.2k
#          stars) + bs32g1038/node-blog + Meowhal/osu-ahr +
